# SOTA Survey

## Search Order
1. arXiv → Semantic Scholar → Google Scholar → Venue proceedings

## 3-Pass Triage
- Pass 1 (2min): title+abstract
- Pass 2 (10min): intro+conclusion
- Pass 3 (60min): full read

## Gap Matrix
| Paper | Method | Dataset | Metric | Limitation |

## Research Quality
- Source hierarchy: peer-reviewed > preprints (established groups) > theses > avoid blogs/AI summaries
- Critical reading: problem significance, novelty, evidence, limitations, reproducibility, citation fairness
- Pitfalls: citation dump, recency bias, authority bias, cherry-picking, scope creep
- Related Work writing: organize by theme, compare don't list, position your work, be fair

## Synthesis Output
- Taxonomy (group by approach)
- Trend timeline
- Gap list → feeds research-question
